" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario.-Credit_-ANASTASIA-SANCHEZ.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario.-Credit_-ANASTASIA-SANCHEZ-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario.-Credit_-ANASTASIA-SANCHEZ-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario.-Credit_-ANASTASIA-SANCHEZ-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario.-Credit_-ANASTASIA-SANCHEZ-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario.-Credit_-ANASTASIA-SANCHEZ-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/The-Lemon-Twigs">柠檬树木</a>的布莱恩·达·阿德达里奥（Brian D&#39;Addario）在他的同名首张个人专辑中分享了他多情的新单曲“直到早晨”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-lemon-twigs-a-dream-is-all-we-know-review-lyrics-tracklist-3751798">柠檬树枝 - “梦想就是我们所知道的”评论：d&#39;Addarios for the Stars</a></strong></li></ul><p>浪漫的曲目让人联想到早期的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kinks">Kinks</a>曲目，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">甲壳虫乐队</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">鲍勃·迪伦（Bob Dylan）</a>的声音融为一体。这首歌以杰出的低音系列，一架曲折的钢琴和d&#39;Addario唱歌：“他们的嘴唇在梦中的光环中包围着我 /他们向我展示了我的眼睛，我的眼睛永远无法看到 /像墓碑Raider一样， Gallali /蜡烛直到早晨才燃烧，”恋爱中的美好时刻。</p><p>由他的兄弟和柠檬树枝的乐队成员迈克尔·达·阿达里奥（Michael D&#39;Addario）执导，“直到伴随视频的录像带，布莱恩（Brian）弹吉他并在叶子包围的公园里唱歌。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Brian D&#39;Addario-直到早晨（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/me-bQt3GF_g?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在新闻稿中谈到这首歌时，布莱恩（Brian）分享道：“这是一首情歌，与那些真实的东西，在所有的噪音和宣传之中，都与那些短暂的时刻有关。 “夜晚是黑色的，直到早晨。”也许事情需要在它们变得更好之前完全崩溃。”</p><p>这首歌标志着Brian即将发行的同名首张个人专辑中的主打单曲。布莱恩（Brian）和迈克尔·德·阿达里奥（Michael D&#39;Addario）都制作了“直到早晨”，并不是出于任何渴望脱离团队的愿望而出生的。迈克尔共同制作了专辑《 Sang Harmony》和《唱片》中的两首歌曲。</p><p> “直到早晨”是在多个工作室和州写的，并由精神渴望，孤立，社会责任，业力和失落的主题结合在一起。布莱恩（Brian）解释说：“当我开始将这张专辑放在一起时，它确实在音乐和主题上挂在一起。这是巴洛克式的国家。” “直到早晨”将于3月20日通过库存记录发布。您可以<a href="https://prescriptionpr.createsend1.com/t/j-l-wlyjtll-iyuukkjddt-t/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3839594" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3839594" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3839594" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Brian d&#39;Addario“直到早晨”专辑艺术品。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Brian-Daddario-Till-The-Morning-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3839594" class="wp-caption-text"> Brian d&#39;Addario“直到早晨”专辑艺术品。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>“直到早晨”的曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1。“直到早晨”</strong><br /> <strong>2。“每个人的歌”</strong><br /> <strong>3。</strong><br /> <strong>4。“有一天我要回家”</strong><br /> <strong>5。“只是为了减轻我的思想”</strong><br /> <strong>6。“锅中的闪光灯”</strong><br /> <strong>7。“公司”</strong><br /> <strong>8。“这个夏天”</strong><br /> <strong>9。“你是美丽的”</strong><br /> <strong>10。“无用的眼泪”</strong><br /> <strong>11。“没有家的精神”</strong></p><p> “直到早晨”还与洛杉矶诗人斯蒂芬·卡利尼奇（Stephen Kalinich）进行了两次合作，他以与海滩男孩的合作而闻名。谈到合作时，布莱恩说：“在洛杉矶扮演我们的一些首场演出后，我在2017年遇到了斯蒂芬。我非常喜欢他的工作，并被他的活力和个性所震惊。他穿着明亮的橙色。用他的话“像南瓜一样！”</p><p> “有一阵子，他向我寄了我的诗，并要求我向他们展示音乐。当我读到“你是美丽的东西”的话时，它感觉很音乐，一旦我拿起吉他，它很容易流动。大约一年后，当他发送“所有人的歌”时，这是同一案例。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGN-48dsvaU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C5